\c 18
\s UMika labakoDani
\p
\v 1 Ngalezonsuku kwakungelankosi koIsrayeli\x + 17.6.\x*; langalezonsuku isizwe sakoDani sazidingela ilifa lokuhlala, ngoba kuze kube ngalolosuku babengawelwanga yilifa phakathi kwezizwe zakoIsrayeli\x + 1.34. Josh. 19.47.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Abantwana bakoDani basebethuma amadoda amahlanu avela kusendo lwabo esuka emaphethelweni abo, amaqhawe, evela eZora leEshitawoli\x + 18.8,11. 13.25. Josh. 15.33.\x*, ukuhlola ilizwe lokuliphenya\x + 1.23. Nani 13.17. Josh. 2.1.\x*. Basebesithi kuwo: Hambani liphenye ilizwe. Asefika entabeni yakoEfrayimi, endlini kaMika, alala khona\x + 17.1,8.\x*.
\v 3 Esendlini kaMika wona alazi ilizwi lejaha umLevi; asephendukela khona athi kuye: Ngubani owakuletha lapha? Njalo wenzani lapha? Njalo ulani lapha?
\v 4 Wasesithi kiwo: UMika ungenzele kanje lakanje; ungiqatshile, sengingumpristi wakhe\x + 17.10.\x*.
\v 5 Asesithi kuye: Ake ubuze\x + Nani 27.21. Hos. 4.12.\x* uNkulunkulu ukuze sazi ukuthi indlela yethu esihamba ngayo izaphumelela yini\x + 17.5. 18.14.\x*.
\v 6 Umpristi wasesithi kibo: Hambani ngokuthula. Indlela yenu elihamba ngayo iphambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 1.17. 1 Kho. 22.6.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 7 Asehamba lawomadoda amahlanu, ayafika eLayishi, abona abantu abaphakathi kwayo, behlezi bonwabile, ngokwendlela yamaSidoni, belokuthula, bengethuki lutho\x + 18.27,28,10. 8.11.\x*, kwakungelamahluleli elizweni ukubathiba, babekhatshana lamaSidoni, bengasebenzelani lamuntu.
\v 8 Asefika kubafowabo eZora leEshitawoli\x + 18.2.\x*, abafowabo basebesithi kuwo: Li\add thi\add*ni?
\v 9 Asesithi: Sukumani asenyuke simelane labo, ngoba sibonile ilizwe\x + Nani 13.30. Josh. 2.23,24.\x*, khangelani-ke, lihle kakhulu; pho lina lithule? Lingavilaphi ukuyangena ukudla ilifa lelizwe\x + 1 Kho. 22.3. Josh. 18.3.\x*.
\v 10 Ekufikeni kwenu khona lizafika ebantwini abonwabileyo lelizweni elibanzi\x + 18.7,27.\x* inhlangothi zombili, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulinikele esandleni senu; indawo lapho okungasweleki lutho khona elizweni\x + Dute. 8.9.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Asesuka lapho evela kusendo lwabakoDani eZora leEshitawoli\x + 18.2.\x* amadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha ehlomile izikhali zempi,
\v 12 enyuka amisa inkamba eKiriyathi-Jeyarimi koJuda\x + Josh. 9.17.\x*. Ngenxa yalokho ayibiza leyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiMahane-Dani\x + 13.25.\x* kuze kube lamuhla; khangela isemuva kweKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + Eks. 3.1.\x*.
\v 13 Asesedlula esuka lapho, aya entabeni yakoEfrayimi, afika endlini kaMika\x + 18.2.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Khona amadoda amahlanu ayehambile ukuhlola ilizwe iLayishi aphendula athi kubafowabo\x + Eks. 23.2 Dute. 26.5. 27.14. 1 Sam. 9.17. 14.28. Jobe 3.2. Isa. 14.10. Zek. 3.4. Seb. 10.46.\x*: Liyazi yini ukuthi kulezizindlu kukhona \w i-efodi\w** lamatherafi lesithombe esibaziweyo lesithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa? Ngakho-ke cabangani elizakwenza\x + 17.4,5.\x*.
\v 15 Asephambukela khona, aya endlini yejaha umLevi endlini kaMika, ambuza impilo.
\v 16 Amadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha ayehlomile ngezikhali zempi, ayengabantwana bakoDani, asesima ekungeneni kwesango\x + 18.11.\x*.
\v 17 Lawomadoda amahlanu ayehambile ukuhlola ilizwe enyuka angena lapho\x + 18.2,14.\x* athatha isithombe esibaziweyo, le-efodi, lamatherafi, lesithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + 17.4,5.\x*, umpristi esemi ekungeneni kwesango lamadoda angamakhulu ayisithupha ayebhince izikhali zempi.
\v 18 La-ke esengenile endlini kaMika athatha isithombe esibaziweyo, i-efodi, lamatherafi, lesithombe esibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa, umpristi wathi kiwo: Lenzani?
\v 19 Asesithi kuye: Thula, bamba umlomo wakho, uhambe lathi\x + Jobe 21.5. Mika 7.16. Jobe 29.9. 40.4. Zaga 30.32.\x*, ube ngubaba kithi lompristi. Kungcono yini ukuthi ube ngumpristi wendlu yomuntu oyedwa kumbe ukuthi ube ngumpristi wesizwe losendo lwakoIsrayeli\x + 17.10.\x*?
\v 20 Lenhliziyo yompristi yathokoza, wasethatha i-efodi lamatherafi lesithombe esibaziweyo, wangena phakathi kwabantu\x + 19.6.\x*.
\v 21 Basebephenduka behamba, babeka abantwanyana lezifuyo lempahla phambi kwabo\x + 1 Sam. 17.22. Isa. 10.28. Seb. 21.15.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Sebekhatshana lomuzi kaMika, amadoda ayesezindlini ezaziseduze lendlu kaMika abizelwa ndawonye abafica abantwana bakoDani.
\v 23 Amemeza abantwana bakoDani. Basebephendula ubuso babo bathi kuMika: Ulani ukuze libuthane?
\v 24 Wasesithi: Lithethe onkulunkulu bami engabenzayo, lompristi, lahamba; pho ngiseselani? Kuyini lokho elikutsho kimi: U\add hlutshwa\add* yini\x + Gen. 31.30.\x*?
\v 25 Abantwana bakoDani basebesithi kuye: Ilizwi lakho kalingezwakali phakathi kwethu, hlezi amadoda alolaka akuhlasele, ulahlekelwe yimpilo yakho lempilo yabendlu yakho.
\v 26 Basebezihambela ngendlela yabo abantwana bakoDani. Lapho uMika esebonile ukuthi balamandla kulaye, waphenduka wabuyela endlini yakhe.
\v 27 Bona basebethatha lokho uMika ayekwenzile lompristi owayelaye, bafika eLayishi ebantwini ababelokuthula bengethuki lutho\x + 18.7.\x*, babatshaya ngobukhali benkemba, batshisa umuzi ngomlilo\x + Josh. 19.47. Dute. 33.22.\x*.
\v 28 Njalo kwakungekho umkhululi, ngoba wawukhatshana leSidoni\x + 18.7.\x*, bengasebenzelani lamuntu. Wawusesihotsheni esasingaseBeti-Rehobi\x + 2 Sam. 10.6. Josh. 19.28.\x*. Basebesakha umuzi, bahlala kiwo.
\v 29 Basebebiza ibizo lomuzi \add ngokuthi\add* yiDani\x + 20.1. Gen. 14.14. Dute. 34.1. 1 Kho. 12.29,30. 15.20.\x* ngebizo likaDani uyise owazalelwa uIsrayeli\x + Gen. 30.6.\x*. Kodwa ibizo lomuzi laliyiLayishi kuqala\x + 18.7.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Abantwana bakoDani basebezimisela isithombe esibaziweyo. Njalo uJonathani indodana kaGereshoma, indodana kaManase\x + Eks. 2.22. 18.3.\x*, yena lamadodana akhe babengabapristi besizwe sakoDani kwaze kwaba lusuku lokuthunjwa kwelizwe\x + 18.31. 13.1. 1 Sam. 4.2,3,10,11. Hlab. 78.60-64.\x*.
\v 31 Basebezimisela isithombe esibaziweyo sikaMika ayesenzile, zonke izinsuku indlu kaNkulunkulu iseShilo\x + 19.18. 20.18,26,31. 21.2,19. 1 Sam. 1.3,7. Josh. 18.1.\x*.
